tools.description:
Get a summary of the active fleet: all vehicle_ids currently in the fleet composition and the optional fleet status.

Returns:
    dict: {
        "success": True,
        "data": {
            "list_of_vehicle_ids": List[str],    # vehicle IDs currently in the active fleet
            "fleet_status": Optional[str],       # fleet status or None
        }
    }
    On error (should not normally occur):
    {
        "success": False,
        "error": str
    }
Notes:
    - If no explicit fleet composition has been configured, all registered vehicles are treated as the active fleet.
